OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776682974
OL,3,CPolice continue to hunt teenager's
OL,4,Ckiller four years after his death
OL,6,FLouis Hackett and Ben Cook were
OL,7,Fcleared of his murder following a
OL,8,Ftrial at Newcastle Crown Court, but
OL,9,FHackett was convicted on manslaughter.
OL,11,FHowever, a judge concluded at the
OL,12,Fhearing that Kieran's killer remains
OL,13,Fat large, saying at the time that
OL,14,F"justice had not been done".
OL,16,FDetective Superintendent Matt Steel,
OL,17,Fthe Senior Investigating Officer for
OL,18,Fthe case, has today (Saturday) urged
OL,19,Fthe public to "do the right thing" and
OL,20,Fhelp them secure closure for Kieran's
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,26,@{D@OOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
