OL,3,CPolice continue to hunt teenager's
OL,4,Ckiller four years after his death
OL,6,FHe said: "Saturday 18 April 2026 marks
OL,7,Ffour years since Kieran disappeared
OL,8,Fand was tragically murdered.
OL,10,F"This was a horrific case where Kieran
OL,11,F` a young man at only 18 years old `
OL,12,Fwas brutally stabbed at least 23 times.
OL,14,F"As ever, our thoughts remain with all
OL,15,Fof Kieran's loved ones as they grieve
OL,16,Ftheir loss, and we remain committed to
OL,17,Fgetting answers for them.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1776682974
OL,3,CPolice continue to hunt teenager's
OL,4,Ckiller four years after his death
OL,6,F"A dedicated team of detectives
OL,7,Fcontinue to review the evidence in
OL,8,Fthis case and follow every avenue to
OL,9,Fidentify any other offenders involved
OL,10,Fin Kieran's murder.
OL,12,F"While one man was found guilty of
OL,13,Fmanslaughter at trial in 2023, our
OL,14,Finvestigation remains very much
OL,15,Factive, and we will continue to follow
OL,16,Fup on any new leads."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
